* 阿布杜·瓦基爾王子（عبدالواقايل Abdul Wakeel）
* 阿美爾拉赫公主（اميايراه ورداتول بولکيه Ameerah Wardatul Bolkiah）

== 六十大寿生日 ==
2006年7月15日，博尔基亚苏丹在斯里巴加湾市的奴鲁伊曼王宫（Istana Nurul Iman إستان نور الأمان ）（Istana在馬來語意為皇宮，Nurul Iman源自阿拉伯語，意為信光）举行了一场举世瞩目的六十大寿生日宴会，共有1万名贵宾出席了寿宴，其中包括[[菲律宾总统|菲律宾总统]][[格洛丽亚·马卡帕加尔-阿罗约|格洛丽亚·马卡帕加尔-阿罗约]]、[[柬埔寨首相|柬埔寨首相]][[洪森|洪森]]、前[[泰国总理列表|泰国首相]][[達新·欽那瓦|他信·西那瓦]]及[[新加坡总理|新加坡总理]][[李显龙|李显龙]]等，[[印度尼西亚|印尼]]和[[马来西亚|马来西亚]]的官员也参加了宴会<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.eastday.com/eastday/node81844/node81854/node149947/u1a2199762.html# |title=苏丹阔绰挥金如土60大寿宴请万名宾客 |access-date=2008-09-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081006061638/http://news.eastday.com/eastday/node81844/node81854/node149947/u1a2199762.html |archive-date=2008-10-06 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[香港|香港]]演员[[曾志偉|曾志偉]]随[[電視廣播有限公司|无线电视]]节目《[[向世界出发|向世界出发]]》外景摄制队到文莱期间也获邀出席宴会，[[電視廣播有限公司|无线电视]]更是唯一香港电子传媒获准拍摄文莱王宫宴会盛况<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://ent.163.com/07/0316/10/39MV3BEP00031H2L.html# |title=曾志伟文莱做“皇帝” |access-date=2008-09-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091129122314/http://ent.163.com/07/0316/10/39MV3BEP00031H2L.html |archive-date=2009-11-29 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 争议 ==
{{main|文莱LGBT权益}}
由于文莱已于2014年落实[[伊斯兰教法|伊斯兰教法]]<ref name="beast">{{cite web |author1=Jay Michaelson |title=Brunei Returns to the Stoning Age |url=https://www.thedailybeast.com/brunei-returns-to-the-stoning-age |publisher=[[每日野兽|每日野兽]] |accessdate=2019-04-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190328004847/https://www.thedailybeast.com/brunei-returns-to-the-stoning-age |archive-date=2019-03-28 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，并计划在2019年4月3日颁布。<ref name="independent">{{cite web |author1=Tom Barnes |title=LGBT+ people to be stoned or whipped to death in Brunei under new sex law |url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/asia/brunei-lgbt-whipping-stoning-gay-people-sharia-law-a8841706.html |publisher=[[独立报|独立报]] |accessdate=2019-04-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190412012001/https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/asia/brunei-lgbt-whipping-stoning-gay-people-sharia-law-a8841706.html |archive-date=2019-04-12 |dead-url=no }}</ref>然而，不少国际政治人物及明星纷纷批评该政策和抵制文莱苏丹的所投资的{{Link-en|多尔切斯特精选酒店|Dorchester Collection}}，这包括[[比佛利山酒店|比佛利山酒店]]和{{Link-en|贝尔艾尔酒店|Hotel Bel-Air}}等汶萊在各國擁有的飯店。<ref name="cnn">{{cite web |author1=Ben Westcott |title=Brunei to punish gay sex and adultery with death by stoning |url=https://edition.cnn.com/2019/03/27/asia/brunei-anti-lgbt-stoning-law-intl/index.html |publisher=[[CNN|CNN]] |accessdate=2019-04-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190412114004/https://edition.cnn.com/2019/03/27/asia/brunei-anti-lgbt-stoning-law-intl/index.html |archive-date=2019-04-12 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Clooney">{{cite web |author1=George Clooney |title=George Clooney: Boycott Sultan Of Brunei’s Hotels Over Cruel Anti-Gay Laws |url=https://deadline.com/2019/03/george-clooney-sultain-of-brunei-hotels-boycott-beverly-hills-hotel-anti-gay-laws-brunei-1202584579/ |publisher=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]] |accessdate=2019-04-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190413034807/https://deadline.com/2019/03/george-clooney-sultain-of-brunei-hotels-boycott-beverly-hills-hotel-anti-gay-laws-brunei-1202584579/ |archive-date=2019-04-13 |dead-url=no }}</ref><REF>
[https://udn.com/news/story/6812/3741308?from=udn-referralnews_ch2artbottom 同性戀死刑激眾怒 名流籲抵制汶萊飯店] {{Wayback|url=https://udn.com/news/story/6812/3741308?from=udn-referralnews_ch2artbottom |date=20190519093735 }} 2019.4.7 聯合
</REF>。

2019年5月5日，博尔基亚宣布，暫緩實施新刑法，並會對相關法律再進行評估<REF>
[https://udn.com/news/story/6809/3796165 國際施壓 汶萊暫緩同志刑罰] {{Wayback|url=https://udn.com/news/story/6809/3796165 |date=20190521125013 }} 2019.5.6 聯合
